---
title: Beef & Mushroom Wellington with Filo Pastry, Mashed Potato, Green Beans & Gravy
description: If you can’t pull together a show-stopping feast at Christmas, when can you? Introducing the star of tonight’s menu, our beef and
mushroom wellington! Wrapped in flaky filo pastry and served with a rich worcestershire gravy, creamy mashed potatoes, and tender steamed green beans, it’s a festive feast that brings warmth and cheer to your table!
